<title>zhǔ tiān tiān kàn gù nǐ 迦南986</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ xiàn zài yào duì nǐ shuō, tiān tiān kàn gù nǐ. zhǔ xiàn zài yào duì nǐ shuō, tiān tiān kàn gù nǐ.
 cháng cháng yǎng wàng zhǔ, bù yào yōu lǜ. zhǔ tiān tiān dōu zài kàn gù nǐ.
 nǐ de xīn zhōng yǐ shēn shēn zhī dào, yī shēng dōu wú fǎ wàng jì.
 jīn shēng jīng lì duō shǎo fēng yǔ, zhǔ tiān tiān dōu zài kàn gù nǐ.</lyrics>
